          "category": "animations",
          "tags": [
            "motion",
            "animations"
          ],
          "bestMatch": 0.18
        },
        {
          "source": "emilkowalski",
          "text": "Slow motion: bump duration 2–5× or use DevTools animation inspector. Check colors crossfade cleanly, easing doesn't stop abruptly, `transform-origin` is right, coordinated properties stay in sync.",
          "suggestedId": "emilkowalski-slow-motion-bump-duration-2-5",
          "category": "animations",
          "tags": [
            "motion",
            "animations"
          ],
          "bestMatch": 0.2
        },
        {
